---
title: Pca - cassav - train vs test 
weave_options:
  error: true
  wrap: false
  term: false
  out_width: 50%
  out_height: 20%
---

```julia
using Jchemo, JchemoData
using JLD2, CairoMakie, GLMakie
```

#### Import data

```julia
path_jdat = dirname(dirname(pathof(JchemoData)))
db = joinpath(path_jdat, "data/cassav.jld2")
@load db dat
@names dat
```

```julia
X = dat.X
@head X
```

```julia
Y = dat.Y
@head Y
```

```julia
year = Y.year 
tab(year)
```

```julia
s = year .<= 2012
Xtrain = X[s, :] 
Xtest = rmrow(X, s) 
ntot = nro(X) 
ntrain = nro(Xtrain) 
ntest = nro(Xtest)
(ntot = ntot, ntrain, ntest)
```

#### Model fit and scores

```julia
model = pcasvd(nlv = 10) 
fit!(model, Xtrain)  
fitm = model.fitm ; 
@head Ttrain = fitm.T 
```

**Project Xtest to the score space**

```julia
@head Ttest = transf(model, Xtest)
```

#### Plot scores

**2-D score space** 

```julia
CairoMakie.activate!()
T = vcat(Ttrain, Ttest)  
group = [repeat(["Train"], ntrain); repeat(["Test"], ntest)]
i = 1
plotxy(T[:, i], T[:, i + 1], group; zeros = true, xlabel = "PC1", ylabel = "PC2").f
```

```julia
color = [(:red, .5), (:blue, .5)]
i = 1
plotlv(T[:, i:(i + 5)], group; size = (750, 400), shape = (2, 3), color = color, zeros = true, xlabel = "PC", ylabel = "PC").f
```

**3-D score space**

```julia
CairoMakie.activate!()  
#GLMakie.activate!()    # for interactive plot
i = 1
plotxyz(T[:, i], T[:, i + 1], T[:, i + 2], group; size = (600, 350), color, markersize = 10, xlabel = "PC$i", ylabel = "PC$(i + 1)", 
    zlabel = string("PC", i + 2), title = "Pca score space").f
```

